, I'm very hesitant towards this patch because Bad Things(tm) happen if numeric user names ever need to be resolved at the system level. (hint: they aren't supported by POSIX.), Thanks [~aw] for your comment. I think you are right but this patch just tries to fix HDFS-4983 problem in reading domain pattern from the configuration and even this problem can happen for non-numeric usernames. 
